{"tid":810343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"o camp遊戲男仔話唔玩會好7？","createTime":"2018-09-08T01:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T17:36:59.000Z","uid":110924,"like":5,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c807f1981b83d4b13aa57ccf1c6b05f1a39b411c","tid":810343,"uid":110924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"條友話唔會玩<br />\n點知同我講一句：全部男仔都玩 唔通得我唔玩<br />\n已經心諗wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要：男人老狗 講到明女朋友唔俾玩好唔知想點又柒 <br />\n<br />\n其實有咩咁㭍🤗？ 俾人知道你有女朋友仲要咁乖 唔係會令其他有女朋友嘅男仔自卑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到一個男仔真係好乖話女朋友唔鍾意 仲要啲人係咁慫恿 佢都堅持唔玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尼啲男仔好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs佢最後冇去到camp 話可以避免 <br />\n但係其實我想佢去測試自己應承我嘅野做唔做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為出到社會一定有更加多人誘惑佢食煙呀叫雞呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家唔經歷遲啲點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都係想知你哋會唔會覺得好柒🤥<br />\n不嬲覺得啲遊戲冇乜嘢 但係佢好雙重標準自己玩得我唔玩得👽我係嬲我真係做到冇玩但係佢應承完反囗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e1a9475235b997f384e67c823bd9595c786318","tid":810343,"uid":110924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"1分鐘都冇有2個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c4c1f9d0a45165b1d5908e786bbe75201ddf30","tid":810343,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05e1a9475235b997f384e67c823bd9595c786318","tid":810343,"uid":110924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"1分鐘都冇有2個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /